=== Immutable Set (Binary Search Tree) ===

Empty set size: 0

=== Adding elements ===
Size after adding 5 elements: 5

=== Adding duplicate ===
Size after adding duplicate 3: 5

=== Contains ===
contains 2: true
contains 4: true
contains 6: false

=== Remove elements ===
After removing 3 and 1:
  size: 3
  contains 1: false
  contains 3: false
  contains 5: true

=== Remove non-existent element ===
After removing non-existent 100:
  size: 3

=== Add from list ===
After adding list [10, 20, 30, 40]:
  size: 4
  contains 10: true
  contains 30: true

=== Union (++) ===
Union of {1,2,3} and {3,4,5}:
  size: 5
  contains 1: true
  contains 3: true
  contains 5: true

=== Intersection (&) ===
Intersection of {1,2,3} and {3,4,5}:
  size: 1
  contains 1: false
  contains 3: true
  contains 4: false

=== Difference (diff) ===
Difference {1,2,3} - {3,4,5}:
  size: 2
  contains 1: true
  contains 2: true
  contains 3: false

=== Select (filter) ===
After selecting x > 2 from {1,2,3,4,5}:
  size: 3
  contains 1: false
  contains 3: true
  contains 5: true

=== Exclude ===
After excluding x > 2 from {1,2,3,4,5}:
  size: 2
  contains 1: true
  contains 3: false

=== Exists ===
exists x => x > 3: true
exists x => x > 10: false

=== All ===
all x => x > 0: true
all x => x > 2: false

=== Fold ===
Sum of all elements: 15

=== Iterator ===
All elements (in order):
  1
  2
  3
  4
  5

=== All tests completed ===
